Text: Transmit Hard Copies Anytime to Anywhere Palm Solutions brought to you by InSync Online Transmit Hard Copies Anytime to Anywhere Dear Jess Youre stuck in evening traffic Your cell phone rings Its your latest sales prospect The one with the multimilliondollar budget Our CEO wants to review your proposal first thing tomorrow Fax me a clean copy would you Its on its way you say Then you fire up Qxprint Talk about convenience in a notquitepaperless world Qxprint essentially turns your wireless Palmtm handheld into a remote control and transmits selected documents from your PC to anyplace in the world Choose Print on demand Fax Email or even express mail to send proposals letters and other important documents It doesnt matter if youre five feet or five hundred miles from your office Qxprint will take care of it You can even upload your contacts to the Qxprint Web site for easy access The price is right tooQxprint charges a nominal fee for each transaction Check it out udrkRVuTZecyUxb The InSync Online Team Must be in Palm Desktop Microsoft Outlook or Goldmine format The content of this message is based on your personal InSync Online profile To modify your profile or unsubscribe from InSync Online return to your InSync Online profile by clicking on the link below Or unsubscribe by replying to this message with unsubscribe as the subject line of the message C Palm Inc All rights reserved udtkRVuTZecyUxQ Palmcom udmkRVuTZecyUxV Palm Store udykRVuTZecyUxK InSync Online insyncdynisZVae MyPalm udikRVuTZecyUxE
